                            <comment id="13015692" author="liyin" created="Tue, 5 Apr 2011 00:05:55 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Sounds good to me.&lt;br/&gt;
But from the code, may be the original purpose of getHRegionInfo is to throw out IllegalArgumentException if the parameter is null, while getHRegionInfoOrNull just return back null if the parameter is null.&lt;/p&gt;
